<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Welcome to Telehealth CRM</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #3B82F6;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #3B82F6;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Telehealth CRM</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @patient.first_name %>!</h2>

      <p>Welcome to our telehealth platform. We're excited to have you as a patient and look forward to providing you with excellent healthcare services.</p>

      <p>Your account has been set up with the following details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @patient.full_name %></li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @patient.email %></li>
        <li><strong>Medical Record Number:</strong> <%= @patient.medical_record_number %></li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>To get started, please set up your password by clicking the button below.</strong> This link will expire in 6 hours.</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= @url %>" class="button">Set Up Your Password</a>
      </div>

      <p>Once you've set your password, you'll be automatically logged in and can access your patient portal to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>View your messages from our healthcare team</li>
        <li>Check your assigned tasks and care plan</li>
        <li>Communicate with your healthcare providers</li>
      </ul>

      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The Telehealth CRM Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
